Having no experience with kids, Ajit recruits Wynton to help him out. Things get a little out of hand when Aiden rolls out - Krakelious. Now, Ajit and Wynton have a tiny Baku-brawler on their hands, with no way to stop him!

title: Darkstar Rising
description: Ben and co. must uncover the truth of a mysterious new villain, Darkstar.

title: Escape from Aggregor
description: Five aliens from another galaxy attempt to escape from their mysterious captor.

title: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik/First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous
description: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik: It's the Haavik Show! Haavik shows up unexpectedly at the practice field and proposes he and Dan play a little game. The Awesome Brawlers have never seen this man before, but they sense something is odd about him. Regardless, when Haavik strokes Dan's ego, there's no way he's backing down from this challenge./First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous: With his back against the wall, Dan tries flipping the script on Haavik by challenging him to a game of his own - a Bakugan Brawl. If Dan wins, then Haavik will have to set him, and the other Awesome Brawler's free.

title: Spin Out
description: Taz learns a tough lesson. He shouldn't spin after eating too much candy.

title: Wrong!
description: On an orchard outing, picking bushels of fresh apples for Granny's home-baked pies, the Baby Looney Tunes encounter Melissa, who is in a mood to tell everyone that her method of apple picking is the only way.

title: So Long, and Thanks for All the Smoothies
description: When Ben and Rook investigate a mysterious alien ghost ship, they discover that Argit and the Vreedle Brothers are fighting for possession of a doomsday device! (Introducing Solid Plugg.)

title: Max Out
description: Gwen's older brother, Ken, disappears and she gets Ben and Kevin to help her track him down. Their investigation leads them to find not only Ken but also another long-missing relative and a startling secret of the DNAliens. This discovery comes at a high cost as Ben is left with greater responsibilities than ever before.

title: Sea Bunnies
description: Oscar discovers an underwater portal. His return ticket? An errand for Susie.

title: Flower Power
description: The babies all want to pick the best flowers for Granny but they end up destroying her garden.

title: Stuck Up, Up and Away/Schoolhouse Rocked
description: Stuck Up, Up and Away: Bratty little Princess comes to town and wants to be a Powerpuff Girl. When she doesn't get what she wants, the girls will have to pay./Schoolhouse Rocked: The Gangreen Gang goes back to school at Pokey Oaks Kindergarten and become the school bullies. Since the girls can't fight in school, how can they stop them?

title: Everett's Trap/Kazami vs. Mc Q
description: Shun and Masato head to Tokyo's Battle Island to discuss plans for hosting public Bakugan battles. Upon landing, they quickly learn it's a set up! The two are now stranded and faced with heaps of brawlers, who are all looking to bring them down!/ Shun and Masato manage to fend off a horde of brawlers on Battle Island, but they quickly learn that was only a diversion- one of Kazami's research centers is under siege. The two must find a way off the island and head off to defend the research center.

title: Oh Brother, Warehouse Art Thou?
description: Baby Sylvester is overcome with angst because Granny's broken old chair, his favorite napping place, must be replaced by a new, unfamiliar piece of furniture. The other Baby Looney Tunes work together to help turn Sylvester's trepidation into enjoyment during their mammoth furniture-shopping adventure.

title: Daffy Did It!
description: Tweety blames Daffy for his mistake, and then has trouble living with the guilt of lying.

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: The Widening Gyre
description: After a giant garbage-like creature appears drags a boat down into the ocean, Ben and the crew investigate the Pacific Garbage Vortex.

title: Save Our Cinnamon
description: Granny's sister's beloved bakery, Cakery Bakery Dock, home of her wonderful trademark cinnamon rolls, is being put out of business so her landlord can tear down the bakery to build a parking lot. This galvanizes the Baby Looney Tunes to work together to bake one giant cinnamon roll as a tourist attraction to save the bakery, a project that ends up involving the whole town.

title: Escape from Family Dinner
description: There's a huge water balloon fight at the creek but Craig is stuck at home for a family dinner, unless he can escape.

title: Yeti Confetti Chapter 4: Lucy's Instrument
description: Lucy goes to Yeti school to find her instrument.

title: The Takeout Mission
description: Kelsey leads her friends on the most important quest ever, picking up takeout for dinner.

title: Hot Air Percy
description: Thomas and Percy are excited to deliver a special balloon for the hot-air balloon festival, but the balloon is wrapped up tight. They're instructed not to peek at it until they arrive. While making the delivery, part of the balloon pops out of its tarp and the wind carries it skyward, along with Percy. Percy never expected to enjoy a flight that much! Now it's up to Thomas to get help from Harold and Beresford in order to bring Percy home.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Inspector #13
description: A mysterious Techadon Master visits Earth, looking for the Ultimatrix. And he turns out to be more dangerous than any Techadon ever imagined.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Chapter 18: Swellington Boots
description: When a summer storm brews, the crew cozies up in the library.

title: The Eggman Cometh
description: When vicious dragons invade Bellwood, it's up to Ben and an all-new alien named Jury Rigg to battle the flying demons and return the peace.

title: Cool for Cats
description: Sylvester believes a commercial that says eating Chewy Chomps will make him cool.

title: Sylvester the Pester
description: An attention-starved Sylvester won't let Granny have any time to herself.

title: Lil' Mac
description: Mr. Gus' nephew terrorizes Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve.

title: The Later Pile
description: Hedgehog convinces Oscar to tackle an overdue errand -- but this time, Oscar's procrastination habit has spooky consequences.

title: Third Time's a Charm
description: Charmaster returns to exact her revenge on Gwendolyn once and for all.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: The Bakugan Battle League Dash/The Final Stage
description: The Bakugan Battle League Dash: With Dan and Ajit eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition, the remaining Awesome Brawlers - Shun, Wynton, Lia and Lightning race to complete the second stage of the competition. The remaining Awesome Brawlers are ready to go, but just as the final round begins, the competitors are surprised with some unwelcome guests.

title: Puddle and the King Chapter 3: All the King's Slides
description: Oscar, Hedgehog and Puddle must figure out what's wrong with the King when he orders the aliens to turn all the planet's sugar into salt.

title: Loose Change
description: Sylvester is upset when Granny paints the bedroom but he learns the importance of change.

title: The Boss
description: Gumball and Darwin help Rocky land an office job so that his dad, Mr. Robinson, will be proud of him. After a health scare the kids decide to reunite Mr Robinson with his son. Mr Robinson has always seen Rocky as a disappointment so when Gumball and Darwin help him land a corporate job at Chanax, he is thrilled. However the Chanax corporation is not quite what it seems. Can Gumball and Darwin rescue Rocky before he becomes a corporate drone for all eternity . . .

title: The Transmogrification of Eunice
description: The team discovers a strange alien girl with no memory but Sunder has been hired to capture her!

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: The Ultimate Sacrifice
description: Ben is suddenly NOT Ben and it's an all-out revolt as the Aliens inside Ben's Ultimatrix demand their freedom.

title: OTTO Motive
description: Kevin and Rook run into an old enemy from the Null Void while attending an intergalactic auto show. (Re-introducing classic Ben alien, Upgrade.)

title: Bakugan Battle Circus/Ebony Manor
description: Shun and Dan head to the Bakugan circus for a little fun, but the fun is interrupted when the star Bakugan are too exhausted to perform. Shun and Dan know the show must go on, and step in to lend a hand. Things go as planned until the evil Ringleader attempts to bring down the big top performance./ Lightning reunites with an old frenemy - Ebony. This time the kitty queen of the streets has a new home and is living a life of luxury with her new master.

title: Cereal Boxing
description: The kids become obsessed with getting the prizes from boxes of sugary cereal.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Time Out!
description: Bugs, Daffy and Taz are disciplined by having a time out in the corner.

title: A Lot Like Lola
description: Lola wants everyone to be more like her until they all start acting exactly like her.

title: A Very Percy Valentine's Day
description: It's Valentine's Day and no one on Sodor is happier than Percy -- he gets to deliver everyone's gifts to their friends throughout the island! This is a lifestyle that he can get used to, but it becomes apparent Agit is torn between a life as a phantom thief and life as a brawler.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers

title: Lights! Camera! Tweety!
description: The Baby Looney Tunes are very eager to visit the local TV station, home of their favorite live children's show. When Floyd accidentally locks them inside the studio moments before airtime, they are forced to put on today's program all by themselves!

title: Chapter 19: Weather Your Weather
description: Susie mulls over her past.

title: The Sandman Is Coming

description: After Bubbles wins two tickets to see the girls' favorite band Sensitive Thugz, Blossom and Buttercup vie for her plus one. But when the Mayor's plane crashes on Monster Island, the girls must put aside their differences to save the day!

title: Kana Recharges

When a big storm reaches Sodor, Kana teaches her friends about the value of spending time alone and "feeling the hush."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

description: Daffy learns a bad word and must learn not to use it.

title: The Creature from the Chocolate Chip
description: Sylvester eats all of Granny's cookies then makes up a cookie monster to blame.

title: Time Heals
description: Gwen travels back in time to prevent the accident that turned Kevin into a monster from ever happening. But she ends up altering history forever.

title: Sandy Versus the Storm

title: Clyde Five

description: The magical creatures work together to send Mildred on a mission so they can have a special bedtime.

description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

Luckily, Beresford the Crane has a plan to aid the Number One Engine! Will they be able to plant the biggest tree before the end of the holiday?
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Speedster Sandy
description: After yet another victorious race, Kana seems unbeatable! No engine on the island is as fast as Kana! However, this does not stop Sandy from challenging the electric engine. By focusing on her own strengths rather than comparing to Kana's strengths, she makes a fast track to victory!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: Chapter 17: Meeting of Mounds
description: The Coven challenges The Cuties to an impromptu softball game.

title: Flu the Coop
description: Baby Bugs and Baby Daffy decide to team up and unlike the other Baby Looney Tunes, fake having received their annual flu shots at the local clinic. The joke's on them when they awaken on the day of Granny's big party unable to have fun because they both have the flu.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Goodbye, Ghost-Scaring Machine
description: Percy announces he's giving up his Ghost Scaring Machine - he's too old for it now. It soon becomes clear that the machine is good for more than just "scaring ghosts."
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Dangerous Dealings/The Hunter Returns
description: Dangerous Dealings: The Awesome Brawler's have become aware of a growing number of adults with illegal Baku-brawling devices. But where are they all coming from? Shun decides to take things into his own hands and sets up a "sting" operation to try to draw out the person selling the devices./The Hunter Returns: Lightning has been caught and locked up by an overly aggressive dog catcher! And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

title: Lighthouse
description: The Bears find a lighthouse powered by a luminous creature.

title: Give Pizza a Chance
description: Rivals Buster and Plucky decide to throw an epic pizza party and are shocked to find out they're actually getting along while Babs and Sweetie get into their first roommate disagreement.

title: Doll's House
description: The Bears apply to be roommates in a fantastic dream dollhouse.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: More Than a Pretty Engine
description: After a fierce storm causes a rockslide in Crumble Canyon, mountain engine Ashima is eager to clean and clear the chaos with her new friends. However, Thomas and the others are concerned: if Ashima were to help them, the mucky mess could ruin her beautiful paint! When the friends' fussiness prevents Ashima from working with the team, she has to prove to Thomas and the others that they shouldn't judge her by her appearance.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: Hall of Mooms
description: Hedgehog tries to get her broom back.

title: The Saint
description: Gumball doesn't believe anyone could really be as nice as Alan and sets out to find his breaking point. Alan is so good-natured that Gumball feels compelled to make him lose his temper. Despite turning the whole school against him, destroying his relationship with Carmen and even selling his parents, Alan remains understanding and happy. Defeated, Gumball and Darwin decide to adopt Alan's positive attitude to see if they can be more like Alan.Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who turns out to be all too real. Anais throws a party but no-one shows up as she has no friends or social skills. Gumball and Darwin help Anais make up an imaginary friend who, much to all their surprise, appears in front of them. Gumball and Darwin teach Anais and her new friend how to become friends but realize he might not be so imaginary after all.

title: Bismuto Casual
description: Perla invita a Bismuto a la pista de patinaje para darle una lección sobre cómo forjar relaciones humanas.

title: The Cake Mistake
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus eat a cake meant for someone else.

title: Tea & Basketball
description: Sylvester wants to play tea with the girls while Lola wants to play basketball with the boys.

title: Yours, Mine...and Mine, Mine!
description: Daffy thinks if he shares his old toys, Granny will buy him all new toys.

title: Song of Sodor
description: When Nia suggests adding a song to spice up Sir Topham Hatt's new bench unveiling, he calls upon her to write a song for the ceremony, but Nia soon finds she may have bitten off more than she can sing.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

description: Daffy feels defeated whenever things aren't going his way.

description: Ben finally manages to rid himself of Skurd... just when he needs the Slime-Biot most.

title: Act Your Age
description: The kids try to see who can act most like a baby, while vying for Granny's attention.

title: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers/The Return of Sophie
description: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers: The Awesome brawlers go to see Benton Dusk to tell him about the Fusion Bakugan and ask him if he knows anything about this character: Haavik. Shun has his hands full when Sophie starts making trouble for Kazami Holdings, accusing them of illegally exploiting Bakugan.

title: The Emily Ghost Institute for Manners and Magical Etiquette
description: Oscar and Hedgehog go to a magical etiquette class.

title: Trouble Busters!/French Fry Wars
description: Trouble Busters!: Now that the Awesome Brawlers are world famous Bakugan experts, they want to help people solve their Bakugan-related problems. When the world's quietest town is experiencing unexplained noises, the Awseome Brawlers are called in to get to the bottom of it./French Fry Wars: The Awesome Brawlers are arguing over who gets to eat the last french-fry. At first, each member makes a case for why they should to be the one to eat it. But the quarrel quickly escalates into trash talk and revealing secrets about one another. With everyone now upset, things take an unexpected turn.

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: Susie and Ramona Chapter 1: Susie's Ark
description: When Susie learns magic is beginning to disappear from New York, she tries to lead all the magical creatures to safety.

title: Ben 10,000 Returns
description: Eon is back and it's up to an older and wiser Ben from the future to help the crew defeat him using the Hands of Armageddon to win the battle.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Now Museum, Now You Don't
description: Their very first trip to an art museum unleashes creative energy, turning the Baby Looney Tunes into enthused culture connoisseurs and budding artists. Baby Bugs recreates the museum experience back at Granny's house, finding abundant art history in everyday objects to the others' sheer delight.

title: Ben 10 Returns Part 1
description: Ben Tennyson is a normal teenager who has put away his toys including the Omnitrix that gave him his powers. Ben's life take a turn when he is attacked by an alien and discovers Grandpa Max is missing. To find his grandpa, Ben teams up with his cousin, Gwen, his grandpa's partner, Magister, and even his former nemesis, Kevin 11. When they discover the Forever Knights (a secret organization that deals in illegal alien technology) and DNAliens (the Highbreeds henchmen) are trading dangerous weapons, Ben decides to once again put on the Omnitrix and quickly learns he can now transform into ten new aliens.

title: El Club Salchicha
description: Perricornio está decidido a convertirse en el rey de los hot dogs y se une al Club Salchicha, una competencia clandestina de comer hot dogs.

title: Blue Engine Blues
description: After getting through a rough night's sleep and finding out his beach day gets cancelled due to the rain, Thomas winds up in the grumpiest of moods. Encountering Riff and Jiff with their usual happy-go-lucky attitudes, Thomas comes to the conclusion that he'll only be liked when he appears happy. He puts on fake smile for the rest of the day, but his words don't match his demeanor and everyone can see right through him. Finally, Thomas comes across Riff and Jiff again, who reveal they're also upset about the cruddy day! They teach him that nobody can be happy all the time, and sometimes you need a friend to vent to on the days you're most blue.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Pepper and the Fog
description: After the island gets covered in fog, Pepper attempts to make it to Susie's house.

title: It Was Them

description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: If All Else Fails
description: A hibernating Highbreed officer awakens and triggers a device designed to destroy the planet. Now Ben must figure out a way to stop him.

title: Did Not! Did Too!
description: Bugs and Lola temporarily decide that they don't want to be friends any longer.

description: Ben and company help the prince of the arachna-chimps, Simian, return to power.

description: Ben goes into the Null Void to aid the Plumber's Helpers defeat D'Void.

title: Imaginary Friend
description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

description: When Thomas and Percy's plan to surprise Diesel goes awry, the two friends still manage to cheer up Diesel... just not in the way they expected!

description: When music-lover Nia gets stranded before a big concert she's been waiting to see, Thomas brings the concert to her!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

title: Betsy and Ghost Chapter 3: There's A Racket In My Hope Chest
description: The witches search for Betsy - who doesn't want to be found. Can she learn to love being a witch as much as she loves being a ghost?

description: Susie, Ramona, and Barb team up in frozen time to see what's threatening magic.

title: Carly's Magnificent Magnet
description: When Carly gets a new magnet to help Tess the Troublesome Crane load up a shipment of metal crates, she struggles with the new tool. originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
